<HEADLINE> Primakov Returns From Hong Kong </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MOSCOW, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Russian Foreign Minister Evgeny
Primakov said today that China's resumption of the exercise of
sovereignty over Hong Kong has profound significance not only for
China itself, but also for the whole world.
</P>
<P>
