delivered to the US congress that China provided "a tremendous
variety of assistance" to ballistic missile programs in Iran and
Pakistan, the Washington Post reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
The CIA report alleged that China is a "primary source of
nuclear-related equipment and technology to Pakistan". 
