Martina Hingis of Switzerland defeating Russia's Anna Kournikova
6-3 6-2.
</P>
<P>
Cedric Pioline of France had also earlier beaten Briton Greg
Rusedski 6-4 4-6 6-4 6-3 in their quarter-final on Court One.
</P>
<P>
This year's championships have been interrupted by rain many
times. 
