<HEADLINE> Bangladeshi Opposition Enforces Half-day Strike Today </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, July 3 (Xinhua) -- The main opposition Bangladesh
Nationalist Party (BNP) today enforced a countrywide half-day
