Parliament on June 30.
</P>
<P>
It was the second major anti-government street protest against
the one-year-old government of Awami (people's) League (AL). The
BNP first enforced a half-day strike on March 23 across the
country to protest, among other issues, the government's pro-India
policy.
</P>
