the countrymen to observe the strike and build a strong resistance
against imposition of taxloads in the budget.
</P>
<P>
She said the government imposed heavy tax and all-grabbing
surcharge on essentials. The ruling party hatched conspiracy to
make the country dependent on others and jeopardize the economy by
imposing new and extended taxes on industrial raw materials,
machinery and spares, she alleged.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, AL General Secretary Zillur Rahman Wednesday accused
the BNP of conducting a "false and shameless campaign" against the
budget in a bid to mislead the people.
</P>
<P>
"They (BNP) are calling it a budget to kill the people while
the budget has given maximum protection to the interests of the
common masses," he told a big rally in Dhaka on Wednesday
afternoon.  
</P>
