<HEADLINE> Albanian Newspaper Hails Hong Kong's Return </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, July 2 (Xinhua) -- Albania's Socialist-controlled
newspaper, the Voice of the People, today hailed the return of
Hong Kong to the motherland in a signed editorial.
</P>
<P>
The return of Hong Kong to China not only has historical
significance for China, but also has great significance for the
current global political situation, the article said.
</P>
<P>
Observing the celebrations of the event in China, the Albanian
people were very excited, the article stated.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong's return shows that the territorial sovereignty,
which the Chinese people have enjoyed since ancient times, can
never be taken away, the article said.
</P>
<P>
Neither occupation by a big country nor agreements and
treaties signed by the two sides can trample underfoot the
people's inalienable rights. 
</P>
